To compile SoundTouch on MacOS:

env CPP=/usr/bin/cpp ./configure --enable-integer-samples CPPFLAGS="-arch i386 -arch ppc -arch x86_64" LDFLAGS="-arch i386 -arch ppc -arch x86_64" --disable-dependency-tracking

To compile SoundTouch on Linux:

(may need to get autoconf, libtool; delete config/m4/*)
./bootstap
./configure --enable-integer-samples CXXFLAGS="-fPIC"
make
make install